# InferTest — expected entailments
# Construct : owl:sameAs (individual identity)

@prefix : <http://example.org/infertest#> .
@prefix rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> .

### MorningStar and EveningStar are the same individual, and MorningStar is
### observed by Astronomer -> so must EveningStar be.
:SameIndividual_EveningStar :sameIndividualObservedBy :SameIndividual_Astronomer .
